data.description: Step into a desert oasis, an appealing 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with a spacious 3 car garage in the thriving Hacienda Del Oro neighborhood! Nestled in an upcoming area of Rita Ranch, this residence offers convenient access to shopping, dining and close proximity to the loop. It seamlessly combines urban amenities with a suburban feel. Embrace the Arizona lifestyle with a generous backyard and mature saguaros, providing a touch of desert elegance. Inside this open floor plan, you'll enjoy the comfort of updated flooring and stainless steel appliances, adding a modern touch to this already inviting home.  Welcome to your new home!
